Brand Character Blueprint

Define the character your brand embodies in the narrative world.

## 1. Brand Archetype

Choose one or hybridize:

The Guide

The Creator

The Rebel

The Caregiver

The Visionary

The Sage

The Hero

The Explorer

## 2. Personality Traits

Write 5–7 traits your brand expresses consistently.

## 3. Voice System

Words you always use

Words you avoid

Rhythm & cadence

Emotional tone

## 4. Character Manifesto

“Our brand shows up as _________ because we believe _________ and we want people to feel __________.”
